reviewText: This DVD will have you making bracelets in no time flat. Everyone of them are so beautiful. People will be commenting on your bracelets saying how beautiful they are and how much talent you have.

I enjoy Sharilyn's videos.  They are technique-packed with simple to do projects.  More advanced wirework is included as well.  I recommend these for anyone interested in increasing their wireworking skills.  They are good for the beginner and the more advanced jeweler as well.
I love her teaching style.  Another great DVD from Sharilyn!  All her stuff is just the best!

Sharilyn does it again with another 5-star DVD - Sharilyn's instruction is very clear and it won't be long before you are making bangles, beaded bangles and half-bangle bracelets, a must for your library.

I recently purchased a copy of Sharilyn Miller's Bohemian Bangles.  It's the third video of Miller's that I've bought.  If you're not familiar with her books a videos you should be.  She's simply the best.  Bohemian Bangles is another winner.  Buy it!
This is a keeper! Love this DVD as well as all of Sharilyn's DVD. Offers a ton of information and direction on different jewelry techniques.

This video is great if you want to create beautiful, fun, wearable bracelets and bangles.  Sharilyn shows you how to make all of these, but also shows you how to get the fit you want and balance and design as well. The videos are clear and easy to follow instructions. The best part is, you'll have great jewerly that you've made entirely with your own hands!
